Detailed Description

The object class for objects passed to the callback during MIP optimization.

Syntax:
   out = CpxInfo(cplex);
Usage:
The CpxInfo object will be passed to the CPLEX® callback during MIP optimization. The callback function is called with such an object as a parameter. Its properties are initialized to represent the current solution/progress of the solve and can be queried by the callback function.
Methods:
See MATLAB® Help for Handle Class to see the methods inherited.
